v - aped 1.x 's extend control-center
-------------------------------------
see extend.png for network skeleton

the server v can handle other aped's following request through udp protocol:

connect     called before CMD_CONNECT, for load balance.

user_on     user online
user_off    user offline

msg_snd     message across aped


depend
------

v currently depend on following libraries:
    clearsilver     http://www.clearsilver.net/
    mevent          https://github.com/bigml/cmoon/tree/master/lib/mevent
    mnl             https://github.com/bigml/cmoon/tree/master/lib/mnl


